  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">CLEAR SCREEN Command</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="__CommandInclude" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Purpose</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Take input from the keyboard and assign it to a memory variable.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Syntax</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">CLEAR SCREEN</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Description</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The command CLEAR erases the screen. <br/>After execution of the CLEAR command, the cursor is positioned at 0, 0 and the functions Row() and Col() are updated. </para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1">Examples</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">This example uses ACCEPT to get keyboard input from the user:</para>
